# Documentation Sync

## Source of Truth

- **AGENT.md** — canonical agent contract. Plan creation/review, execution loop, blocking.
- **docs/cli-reference.md** — CLI commands and options. Must match actual `tg` behavior.
- **docs/agent-contract.md** — detailed version; keep aligned with AGENT.md.

## Update Triggers

- **New CLI option or command** → update `docs/cli-reference.md`
- **Agent workflow change** → update AGENT.md and `docs/agent-contract.md`
- **New import format or plan format** → update `docs/plan-import.md`
- **Schema or architecture change** → update `docs/schema.md` or `docs/architecture.md`

## Rule

When adding or changing features that affect user/agent behavior, update the relevant docs in the same change.
